rts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-100-biggest-songs-of-2014-revealed-3386/ |title=The Official Top 100 Biggest Songs of 2014 revealed |first=Rob |last=Copsey |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]] |accessdate=January 1, 2015 |date=December 31, 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231184716/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-100-biggest-songs-of-2014-revealed-3386/ |archivedate=December 31, 2014 }}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|88\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2014/hot-100-songs |title=Hot 100 Songs \u2013 Year End 2014 |work=Billboard |accessdate=2014-12-09 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210021449/http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2014/hot-100-songs |archivedate=December 10, 2014 }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|46\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US Adult Contemporary (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2014/adult-contemporary-songs|title=Adult Contemporary Songs \u2013 Year-End 2014|work=Billboard|accessdate=August 26, 2019}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|11\n|}\n\n===Decade-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2010\u20132019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ariacharts.com.au/annual-charts/2019/end-of-decade-singles-chart|title=2019 ARIA End of Decade Singles Chart|publisher=ARIA|accessdate=January 16, 2020}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK Singles (Official Charts Company)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-uks-official-top-100-biggest-songs-of-the-decade-2010-2019__27936/|title=The UK's Official Top 100 biggest songs of the decade|publisher=Official Charts Company|last=Copsey|first=Rob|date=December 11, 2019|accessdate=December 12, 2019}}</ref>\n| 67\n|-\n! scope=\"